#

Chicken Burrito Bowl

30 min
$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthyMexican

Description

A delicious and customizable bowl filled with tender chicken, fluffy rice, fresh veggies, and zesty toppings.

Ingredients

  • boneless, skinless chicken breast: 1 pound
  • cooked rice (white or brown): 2 cups
  • black beans (canned): 1 can (15 oz)
  • corn (canned or frozen): 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • avocado: 1
  • shredded cheese (cheddar or mexican blend): 1 cup
  • salsa: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • taco seasoning: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro (optional): for garnish
